<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١١٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(ولا)</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span> أغزو على <span class="c2">(أجر)</span> <span class="c2">(٧)</span> <span class="c2">(٨)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
